<span id="freeTextContainer2327380822642661845">I had the pleasure of (briefly) talking about this book, which has always meant the world to me, on the BBC in commemoration of Didion&apos;s passing. It retains its raw power, and the ending is an all-timer. <a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1XuaQ_56B5o'>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1XuaQ...</a></span>
  <span id="freeText2327380822642661845" style="display:none">I had the pleasure of (briefly) talking about this book, which has always meant the world to me, on the BBC in commemoration of Didion's passing. It retains its raw power, and the ending is an all-timer. <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1XuaQ_56B5o">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1XuaQ...</a></span>
